{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"58d04143f0","title":"邓小平在西楼会议上的发言","origin":"《反革命修正主义分子邓小平反动言论》（北京大学文化革命委员会资料组，一九六七年十月）","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3881cc5160","index":0,"year":1962,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"58d04143f0"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f0e44655bb","name":"邓小平"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bdb2925aff","type":"title","text":"邓小平在西楼会议上的发言","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"432de7175e","type":"authors","text":"邓小平","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"a954ce9a23","type":"subtitle","text":"（一九六二年三月，摘录）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"b20db2d055","type":"paragraph","text":"谈到如何控制劳动工资和亏损企业时，邓平说：“财政、银行要卡死，不要怕工人打扁担，厂长打跑了，免得我们撤换。这样严格了，就可以逼他们搞经济核算。现在要恢复象1953年以前那样的制度。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"91950ac023","type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×  ×  ×","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"62ab30a559","type":"paragraph","text":"办法要得用，要少。如高级品。总之不能多，要搞真正捞到东西的。点子太多，作用不大。延期付款的买卖不能多做，否则积在一起，转不过来。办法有三条：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"f9e0b2ded6","type":"paragraph","text":"1.根本办法在于减人。主要表现在建设速度放慢。这不会得罪人，无非是对外名誉不好。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"3c5851c8a6","type":"paragraph","text":"2.真正抓点生活用品，回笼票子。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"deeb4411d9","type":"paragraph","text":"3.制度搞严，漏洞堵死，措施要落实，能顶多少是多少。保经济作物，少而精，拿点粮食，烟叶。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"b84aa71bfb","type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×  ×  ×","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"6edb4a1828","type":"paragraph","text":"现在要恢复到1954年那样，管得死死的，搞一段再说。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"af61f7f334","type":"paragraph","text":"几个办法：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"44bc95bda6","type":"paragraph","text":"1.节约一切能节约的资金，但钱不一定很多，可以变风气。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"200a2abf3f","type":"paragraph","text":"2.农村投放，过去剥削农民多（了），这几年是否给农民多了。提价赔退都过分了，再加上集市贸易更多了。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"1143a8363e","type":"paragraph","text":"3.基本建设和生产的关系。可否两三年内基本停止基建，只有两种：（1）维持再生产；（2）保护工程。只搞这两项，连国防也可考虑停下来。把市场转过来，再来搞。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"ca79419026","type":"paragraph","text":"煤炭、矿山、森林、有色金属缺门不能停。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"00dd504745","type":"paragraph","text":"生产，首先搞零配件，拖拉机应该首先要搞零配件。主要搞生活资料。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"e7224460c5","type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×  ×  ×","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"d5e1b8acaf","type":"paragraph","text":"有人谈到财政、银行、农业正在搞制度时，邓小平插话说“一百条不要多花精力（指商业100条），要搞经营管理制度，写几条，什么难办，什么不难办，不要写得很多。财政、银行也是如此。”","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"eb01df716c","type":"paragraph","text":"有人谈到准备明年（63年）调整物价调整工资时，邓小平插话说“可以考虑，生产多一点，物价提50%，工资提50％，但关键在工业品。”","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"89274d988b","type":"paragraph","text":"刘少奇谈到基建除了某些必要的外都停止时，邓小平插话说“国防基建，也要紧缩一下”。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0"}],"page":{"id":"c18e3cda09","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"58d04143f0","start":0,"end":0}},"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"01a79de6bd","type":"paragraph","text":"1.根本办法在于减人。主要表现在建设速度放慢。这不会得罪人，无非是对外名誉不好。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"177eebb84a","type":"paragraph","text":"刘少奇谈到基建除了某些必要的外都停止时，邓小平插话说“国防基建，也要紧缩一下”。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"29d25b9176","type":"paragraph","text":"有人谈到准备明年（63年）调整物价调整工资时，邓小平插话说“可以考虑，生产多一点，物价提50%，工资提50％，但关键在工业品。”","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"2c0a56bdde","type":"paragraph","text":"办法要得用，要少。如高级品。总之不能多，要搞真正捞到东西的。点子太多，作用不大。延期付款的买卖不能多做，否则积在一起，转不过来。办法有三条：","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"4c40fd6d59","type":"paragraph","text":"3.制度搞严，漏洞堵死，措施要落实，能顶多少是多少。保经济作物，少而精，拿点粮食，烟叶。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"67b916b05d","type":"paragraph","text":"谈到如何控制劳动工资和亏损企业时，邓平说：“财政、银行要卡死，不要怕工人打扁担，厂长打跑了，免得我们撤换。这样严格了，就可以逼他们搞经济核算。现在要恢复象1953年以前那样的制度。”","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"6cb5ec55c4","type":"paragraph","text":"生产，首先搞零配件，拖拉机应该首先要搞零配件。主要搞生活资料。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"6d09bed190","type":"paragraph","text":"2.真正抓点生活用品，回笼票子。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"6f35d0ab79","type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×  ×  ×","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"76d6e2a91d","type":"paragraph","text":"2.农村投放，过去剥削农民多（了），这几年是否给农民多了。提价赔退都过分了，再加上集市贸易更多了。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"96eda4fc89","type":"authors","text":"邓小平","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"a422b0947f","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六二年三月，摘录）","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"58d04143f0"},{"id":"a908dfc95e","type":"paragraph","text":"几个办法：","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","